  "original_title": "Tesla Bot \u0db1\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd6\u0db4\u0dd3 \u0dbb\u0ddc\u0db6\u0ddd\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A humanoid robot named Tesla Bot",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At the end of Tesla's 2021 AI Day event related to the year 2021, Tesla recently worked to introduce a concept of a humanoid robot powered by AI technology.",
        "This introduction has attracted the attention of many people, and the reason for this is that the concept of a robot that walks among humans in the world built by humans, that is, a robot that is friendly and very cooperative with humans, is presented through this.",
        "At the end of the AI \u200b\u200bday event, after a dance of a woman dressed as a Tesla Bot, Elon Musk disclosed about this latest Tesla Bot project, which is expected to launch a prototype \"mostly next year\".",
        "According to Musk, the humanoid robot, which is 5 feet 8 inches tall and weighs 57 kilograms, will be manufactured using lightweight materials and will be able to see complete data about the robot from a screen that will be placed \"somewhere on the robot's body.\"",
        "The robot will be designed to perform \"unsafe, repetitive and boring\" tasks for humans that should be performed by humans.",
        "Musk pointed out something like \"going to a grocery store and getting stuff\" as an example, and thus, it can be expected that in the future, humans will have to work physically but \"do not need to do so\"."
      ],
